    * Scroll down and click the green **Commit changes** button.
  
  
    Navigate back to the main page of your repository and click on the `version.json` file you just created.
    * Look for a button near the top right of the file preview that says **Raw**. Click it.
    * Your browser will load a plain text page containing only your JSON.
    * Copy the URL from your browser's address bar. It will start with `https://raw.githubusercontent.com/...`
  
  
    Open your `pcgt_launcher.py` script. Locate the `OTAUpdateWorker` class.
    * Replace the placeholder URL with the raw URL you just copied.
    
    ```python
    # Before
    self.manifest_url = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YOUR_NAME/PCGT/main/version.json"
    
    # After
    self.manifest_url = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GhozianVanya/PCGT/main/version.json" 
    ```
